   Extended Golay [|BT|, h(E6), KEY1^3] = [24,12,8]
   ALL parameters are tournament vocabulary!

3. MUSIC THEORY:
   Pythagorean intervals = 2^a * 3^b (LITERALLY KEY1 and KEY2!)
   Chromatic scale: h(E6) = 12 notes
   Diatonic scale: H_forb_1 = 7 notes
